parameters:
\nw[Taro]Are earth beasts really that big!? It's like a
whole mountain!

\nw[Kuno]Is it shaking because that thing is moving?! It's
a little too dangerous, don't you think?!

\nw[???]You guys got in the way and ended up reviving me,
didn't you?! Geez, geez!!

\nw[Taro]What are you saying? You're the one who revived
me, right?!

\nw[???]Huh?! What are you saying? It was you guys who
forcibly interrupted the sealing ritual earlier!

\nw[???]That's right! It's a ritual to cut off the supply
of magic and release the magic that the earth
beasts have accumulated for their revival!

\nw[???]It seems like the interruption earlier caused the
disruption of the magic supply. Geez, how much
effort do you think we put into gathering the
magic for the ritual!

\nw[Kuno]Huh... Weren't you trying to revive the earth
beasts?

\nw[???]Huh? Why did you think that? Did I say something
like that?

\nw[Taro]No, I didn't say that... But we were performing
some kind of ritual, and this is the temple
related to the earth beasts.

\nw[Taro]Moreover, it seems like they were gathering
magical power in various places, and they were
doing it in a way that inconvenienced people, so I
wondered if they were planning something...

\nw[???]What are you saying? Originally, we were going
around the nearby towns asking for cooperation
with the magical power.

\nw[???]We just had to change our methods and gather
magical power in order to seal them because no
important person from anywhere was willing to
cooperate, even though we said we needed the magic
for the revival of the earth beasts.

\nw[???]So you didn't want to revive the earth beasts
either? Honestly, interfering with a
misunderstanding like this, how are you going to
make it up to us!

\nw[???]Once they're revived, we won't be able to seal
them again unless we defeat them!

\nw[???]If it was just a misunderstanding, then leave us
alone! We still have magical power left that we
were planning to use for sealing. This will
temporarily immobilize the earth beasts.

\nw[???]It just temporarily stopped moving. I just woke up
and I'm still groggy, so it had an effect, but I
don't know how long it will last.

\nw[???]It's not a problem that can be solved by
apologizing! I'll figure out a way to deal with
that, so I need your cooperation!

\nw[Taro]Even if you say that, is there any way to deal
with that...?

\nw[???]I'll figure something out! I've been working hard
without taking a break for months to gather magic
power, and you've just wasted it all!

\nw[Taro]Alright, let's go back for now. There's no point
in worrying about it here...

\nw[Taro](Is there really a way to defeat a monster as big
as a mountain...?)

\nw[Taro]It's inconvenient not knowing each other's names,
isn't it? I'm Taro, what about you?

\nw[???]Yeah, that's right. If we're going to work
together, we should introduce ourselves.

\nw[Taro](I've been preoccupied with various things, but if
I can go back with this person, I can fulfill the
purpose of coming here! I need to have Prae
checked...!)

I feel the presence of a strong opponent ahead...
Should we proceed?

\nw[Kuno]Are you using some kind of magic? A ritual or
something?
\nw[Taro]Do you know what kind of effect it has, Thors?

\nw[Thorz]Of course I don't know. But we've been using it
for a long time, so maybe it's a large-scale
ritual?

\nw[Taro]Could it be... Are you trying to revive the Earth
Beast?

\nw[Taro]Hey, stop! What are you going to do by reviving
the Earth Beast!

\nw[Taro]Damn, I was so focused that I didn't hear your
voice.

\nw[Kuno]If we try to approach, the dragon will get in the
way. We won't be able to get close unless we
defeat it.

\nw[Taro]Ah, there's no choice but to defeat it... Let's
go!

\nw[Taro]Alright, it stopped moving. I'll stop it right
away!
\nw[???]Who the hell is it!? That hurt out of nowhere!

\nw[???]Ah~ It's those guys who came to bother us before.
Did they come to bother us again?

\nw[Taro]It's obvious that you're being a nuisance. What
are you doing here?

\nw[???]What do you mean? It's obvious that we're
performing a ritual. Besides, we've finally
gathered enough magic power...

\nw[???]Wait, the magic ritual got interrupted. Ah~ Geez,
how far did we progress...
\nw[Taro]Hey, don't try to use magic again!

\nw[???]Ugh, so annoying! We don't have time for this! If
we don't hurry, we won't make it in time!

\nw[???]I'll take care of you later, so don't get in the
way!
\nw[Taro]So I told you to stop that!

\nw[???]Did you come to bother us? Ugh, we'll even defeat
your pets... If we're delayed here like this...

\nw[Taro]The ground is shaking... Could it be that the
ritual is already over...?
\nw[Taro]Hey, wait! Don't do whatever you want...
\nw[Kuno]That crystal, it's showing some kind of image!
